---
title: New England Salmon with Foil Pouch Potatoes
description: Transport yourself to a tiny coastal city off the east coast with tonight's New England-inspired salmon dinner. Old Bay seasoned salmon gets the foil-packet treatment with tender leeks and snap peas. Potatoes get roasted alongside for an easy-breezy clean-up!
